messages.content: Hello! To assist us in scheduling appointments effectively, could you please take a moment to fill out the following form? We need details such as the client's name, the date and time of the appointment, and any additional notes. Your input is crucial for our organization and planning. Thank you!

client_name.description: Name of potential client. If not present, return None
client_name.title: Client Name

date.description: Extract the date of appointment. If not present, return None
date.title: Date

time.description: Time of appointment. If not present return None
time.title: Time

notes.description: Any additional notes about the appointment. If not present, return None
notes.title: Notes

appointments.description: Extract the list of appointments scheduled with potential clients. If it doesn't exist, return None
appointments.title: Appointments
